    </item>
    <item>
      <title>了解酒店业对行业就业市场的看法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/catch-hospitality-s-remm-on-industries-job-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Catch Hospitality Group Productions 合伙人兼联合创始人 Eugene Remm 表示，疫情期间失去的工作岗位不会再回来，该行业已经学会了用更少的资源做更多的事情。他在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/catch-hospitality-s-remm-on-industries-job-market-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:37:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场正在超前发展：瑞银的法尔科尼奥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/bond-market-is-getting-ahead-of-itself-ubs-s-falconio-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银应税固定收益策略主管 Leslie Falconio 认为债券市场正在超前发展。贝莱德美洲首席投资和投资组合策略师 Gargi Chaudhuri 表示，劳动力市场正在降温，增长正在正常化，“这正是收益率曲线所反映的。”他们在“彭博实际收益率”节目中采访了 Sonali Basak。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/bond-market-is-getting-ahead-of-itself-ubs-s-falconio-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:27:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尼耶是法国解决债务问题的新希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/french-economy-latest-barnier-is-new-hope-to-square-debt-circle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 正在掌控法国经济，但他面临着一项几乎不可能完成的任务：在财政纪律的需要与要求财政纪律遵守的巨大政治压力之间寻找平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/french-economy-latest-barnier-is-new-hope-to-square-debt-circle</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最新就业数据未能解决美联储关于九月降息的争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/newest-jobs-data-fail-to-resolve-fed-debate-over-september-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国劳动力市场的最新情况为美联储开始大幅降息留下了可能性，尽管周五两位关键官员并未在本月的会议上支持采取此举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/newest-jobs-data-fail-to-resolve-fed-debate-over-september-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的卡鲁伊：已经出台了很多宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/a-lot-of-easing-has-been-delivered-goldman-sachs-karoui</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席信贷策略师 Lotfi Karoui 表示，资本市场已经实施了许多宽松政策，而 Richard Bernstein Advisors 固定收益总监 Michael Contopoulos 则表示，我们不应该买入高风险债券。他们就“彭博实际收益率”与 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/a-lot-of-easing-has-been-delivered-goldman-sachs-karoui</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
